rward to the most. My teacher was amazing and encouraged me to pursue it in college, and so I did. I admitted into college as a Studio Art major with an emphasis on drawing and painting, I loved every bit of it. It felt like I was re-discovering my 7 year old self.","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":2910},"end":{"line":25,"column":381,"offset":3290},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":2910},"end":{"line":25,"column":381,"offset":3290},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"html","title":null,"url":"./nujabes.jpg","alt":"Prayash Thapa Effulgence Nujabes Drawing","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1,"offset":3292},"end":{"line":27,"column":59,"offset":3350},"indent":[]},"value":"\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ead2c1b1ac12ffbcc226064243d02793-41bfa.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; z-index: -1; display: block; \"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 100%;position: relative; width: 100%; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Prayash Thapa Effulgence Nujabes Drawing\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ead2c1b1ac12ffbcc226064243d02793-41bfa.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ead2c1b1ac12ffbcc226064243d02793-d894e.jpg 173w,\n/static/ead2c1b1ac12ffbcc226064243d02793-97c21.jpg 345w,\n/static/ead2c1b1ac12ffbcc226064243d02793-41bfa.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    "},{"type":"text","value":"\n","positio